headline.print_headline: Hamilton Will Come Back Stronger, Says Button
headline.main: Hamilton Will Come Back Stronger, Says Button

lead_paragraph: Nico Rosberg had better brace for the backlash from Lewis Hamilton after ending his Mercedes team mate's run of four wins in a row and taking the Formula One championship lead.
